micro:bit Internet Button


        [micro:bit]                      [ESP-WROOM-32]
  button A -> send BLE packet A  =>  BLE recv -> call Web API A  
  button B -> send BLE packet B  =>  BLE recv -> call Web API B  

demo:
https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BxjmZNQVvhO0NGJZbF9MZmk0dnM

blog:
http://dsas.blog.klab.org/archives/2017-08/52280315.html (in Japanese)

